Alerts and popups :

three types of alert:
-> simple alert (in this we have only 1 option that is ok)
-> Confirmation Alert (in this we have 2 option that is ok or cancel to accept or to dismiss)
-> prompt alert ( in this we have to provide a prompt then we have 2 option ok or cancel)


these javascript alert we can not inspect so this is why we are handling them this way

first we need to switch to alert then do action
alert=driver.switch_to.alert
alert.accept()                    #to accept means to click on ok
alert.dismiss()                   #to reject means to click on cancel

